        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Click to Quit Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires an online platform (e.g., a social network or search engine) to provide an easy-to-use, understandable, and conspicuous mechanism by which a user may delete or otherwise terminate their account on the platform. </p> <p>The Federal Trade Commission must enforce this requirement and treat any violation of the requirement as an unfair or deceptive act or practice.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
